    "Memories are where your tickets come together. Group them by trip, event, or place — whatever you want to remember." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "In Erinnerungen sammeln sich deine Tickets. Gruppiere sie nach Reise, Ereignis oder Ort — was immer du festhalten willst."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Memories are where your tickets come together. Group them by trip, event, or place — whatever you want to remember."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En los recuerdos se reúnen tus billetes. Agrúpalos por viaje, evento o lugar — lo que quieras guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les souvenirs regroupent vos billets. Organisez-les par voyage, événement ou lieu — tout ce que vous voulez garder en mémoire."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nei ricordi i tuoi biglietti si uniscono. Raggruppali per viaggio, evento o luogo — tutto ciò che vuoi ricordare."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "思い出はチケットを集める場所。旅行・イベント・場所など、残したいテーマでグループにしよう。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "추억은 티켓이 모이는 곳이에요. 여행, 이벤트, 장소 — 간직하고 싶은 무엇이든 묶어 보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "回忆将你的车票汇集在一起。按行程、活动或地点归类——任何你想纪念的瞬间。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
