    "This info doesn't need to be accurate — you're not making a real ticket. Only airport codes must be real, to draw the path." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Angaben müssen nicht exakt sein — du erstellst kein echtes Ticket. Nur die Flughafencodes müssen stimmen, damit die Route gezeichnet werden kann."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This info doesn't need to be accurate — you're not making a real ticket. Only airport codes must be real, to draw the path."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Estos datos no tienen que ser exactos — no estás creando un billete real. Solo los códigos de aeropuerto deben ser reales, para dibujar la ruta."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ces infos n'ont pas besoin d'être exactes — vous ne créez pas un vrai billet. Seuls les codes aéroports doivent l'être, pour tracer le trajet."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Queste informazioni non devono essere esatte — non stai creando un biglietto reale. Solo i codici aeroportuali devono essere veri, per tracciare il percorso."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "情報は正確でなくても構いません — 本物のチケットを作るわけではないからです。経路を描くために、空港コードだけは正しく入力してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "정확하지 않아도 괜찮아요 — 실제 티켓을 만드는 게 아니에요. 경로를 그리려면 공항 코드만 정확하면 돼요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些信息无需准确——你并非在创建真实车票。只有机场代码需真实,用于绘制航线。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
