    "You both benefit from an extra memory slot. Need more? Upgrade to Lumoria Premium and create unlimited memories." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the benefits of upgrading to Lumoria Premium.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ihr beide bekommt einen zusätzlichen Erinnerungs-Slot. Mehr gefällig? Wechsle zu Lumoria Premium für unbegrenzte Erinnerungen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You both benefit from an extra memory slot. Need more? Upgrade to Lumoria Premium and create unlimited memories."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ambos obtenéis un hueco extra para recuerdos. ¿Quieres más? Pásate a Lumoria Premium y crea recuerdos sin límite."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vous gagnez chacun un emplacement de souvenir supplémentaire. Vous en voulez plus ? Passez à Lumoria Premium pour créer des souvenirs sans limite."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ricevete entrambi uno slot ricordo in più. Ne vuoi altri? Passa a Lumoria Premium per ricordi illimitati."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "おふたりそれぞれに思い出の枠がひとつ増えます。もっと必要ですか? Lumoria Premium にアップグレードすれば思い出は無制限に。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "두 분 모두 추억 공간이 하나씩 늘어나요. 더 필요하세요? Lumoria Premium으로 업그레이드하고 추억을 무제한으로 만들어 보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你们双方都会多获得一个回忆位。想要更多?升级到 Lumoria Premium,畅享无限回忆。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
